#: ../../content/support.md:1
msgid "Support and assistance"
msgstr "Support et assistance"

#: ../../content/support.md:4
msgid ""
"Contact LPLG support for Resthome (nursing home software for MR/MRS) — open "
"a ticket, what information to include, and where to find help."
msgstr ""
"Contacter le support LPLG pour Resthome (logiciel de maison de repos MR/MRS)"
" — ouvrir un ticket, informations à joindre, où trouver de l'aide."

#: ../../content/support.md:7
msgid ""
"A problem or a question about Resthome? Here is how to get help, from the "
"fastest to the most direct."
msgstr ""
"Un souci, une question sur Resthome ? Voici comment obtenir de l'aide, du "
"plus rapide au plus direct."

#: ../../content/support.md:10
msgid "1. Search the documentation first"
msgstr "1. Cherchez d'abord dans la documentation"

#: ../../content/support.md:12
msgid "Most answers are already here:"
msgstr "La plupart des réponses sont déjà ici :"

#: ../../content/support.md:14
msgid ""
"The **search** at the top of the page (magnifying glass icon): type a "
"keyword, a **code** (e.g. \"931\", \"MDA\"), or an error message."
msgstr ""
"La **recherche** en haut de page (icône loupe) : tapez un mot-clé, un "
"**code** (par ex. « 931 », « MDA »), ou un message d'erreur."

#: ../../content/support.md:16
msgid "The [FAQ](faq.md) and the [Glossary](glossaire.md)."
msgstr "La [FAQ](faq.md) et le [Glossaire](glossaire.md)."

#: ../../content/support.md:17
msgid ""
"The topic guides: [billing](facturation/index.md), "
"[eFact](ehealth/efact.md), [insurability (MDA)](ehealth/mda.md), [agreements"
" (eAgreement)](ehealth/eagreement.md)."
msgstr ""
"Les guides par thème : [facturation](facturation/index.md), "
"[eFact](ehealth/efact.md), [assurabilité (MDA)](ehealth/mda.md), [accords "
"(eAgreement)](ehealth/eagreement.md)."

#: ../../content/support.md:21
msgid ""
"The troubleshooting pages resolve most common cases: [eFact "
"rejections](ehealth/efact-rejets.md), [MDA errors](ehealth/mda-erreurs.md), "
"[Agreement refused](ehealth/eagreement-refus.md)."
msgstr ""
"Les pages de dépannage règlent la majorité des cas courants : [Rejets "
"eFact](ehealth/efact-rejets.md), [Erreurs MDA](ehealth/mda-erreurs.md), "
"[Accord refusé](ehealth/eagreement-refus.md)."

#: ../../content/support.md:25
msgid "2. Open a ticket with LPLG support"
msgstr "2. Ouvrir un ticket au support LPLG"

#: ../../content/support.md:27
msgid "If the documentation is not enough, contact our team:"
msgstr "Si la documentation ne suffit pas, contactez notre équipe :"

#: ../../content/support.md:29
msgid ""
"**Email: [support@lplg.eu](mailto:support@lplg.eu)** — each message "
"automatically opens a tracking **ticket**."
msgstr ""
"**E-mail : [support@lplg.eu](mailto:support@lplg.eu)** — chaque message "
"ouvre automatiquement un **ticket** de suivi."

#: ../../content/support.md:31
msgid ""
"The **Support** button at the bottom right of every page brings you here."
msgstr "Le bouton **Support** en bas à droite de chaque page vous amène ici."

#: ../../content/support.md:33
msgid "For a fast reply, please specify"
msgstr "Pour une réponse rapide, précisez"

#: ../../content/support.md:36
msgid "The **name of your facility**."
msgstr "Le **nom de votre établissement**."

#: ../../content/support.md:37
msgid ""
"What you were doing and the **screen** involved — a **screenshot** helps a "
"lot."
msgstr ""
"Ce que vous faisiez et l'**écran** concerné — une **capture d'écran** aide "
"beaucoup."

#: ../../content/support.md:38
msgid "The exact **error message** or the **code** (eFact, MDA, eAgreement…)."
msgstr ""
"Le **message d'erreur** exact ou le **code** (eFact, MDA, eAgreement…)."

#: ../../content/support.md:39
msgid ""
"The billing **period** or the **resident** involved (internal reference)."
msgstr ""
"La **période** de facturation ou le **résident** concerné (référence "
"interne)."

#: ../../content/support.md:42
msgid "Sensitive data (GDPR)"
msgstr "Données sensibles (RGPD)"

#: ../../content/support.md:45
msgid ""
"Avoid sending a **NISS** or complete medical data by email unless necessary."
" An **anonymized screenshot** is usually enough — hide the name and the "
"national number."
msgstr ""
"Évitez d'envoyer un **NISS** ou des données médicales complètes par e-mail "
"sauf nécessité. Une **capture d'écran anonymisée** suffit le plus souvent — "
"masquez le nom et le numéro national."

#: ../../content/support.md:50
msgid "Further reading"
msgstr "Pour aller plus loin"

#: ../../content/support.md:52
msgid "[FAQ](faq.md) · [Glossary](glossaire.md)"
msgstr "[FAQ](faq.md) · [Glossaire](glossaire.md)"

